<h1>Your Appointment</h1>

<h2>Thank you, <%= @appointment.mentee_name %></h2>
<h2>Your appointment is scheduled for <%= @appointment.date_start_time.strftime("%I:%M %p") %> on  <%= @appointment.date_start_time.strftime("%a %v") %> and will last for <%= @appointment.duration %> minutes with <%= @appointment.mentor.full_name %>.</h2>

<a href="mailto:<%= @appointment.mentor.email %>,<%= @appointment.mentee_email %>?subject=1871 appointment cancellation&body=I'm sorry but I am unable to make the appointment that was scheduled on <%= @appointment.date_start_time.strftime("%a %v") %> at <%= @appointment.date_start_time.strftime("%I:%M %p") %> . Please make any appropriate changes in your calendar. Thank you!" class="b-tooltip" title="Email"><h4>Cancel Appointment via Email</h4><i class="fa fa-envelope"></i></a><h4>Please give at least 24 hours notice.</h4>

  </body>
</html>